	"data": "<div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>لِّلرِّجَالِ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> نَصِيبٞ مِّمَّا تَرَكَ ٱلۡوَٰلِدَانِ وَٱلۡأَقۡرَبُونَ وَلِلنِّسَآءِ </div><div>نَصِيبٞ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>مِّمَّا</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> تَرَكَ ٱلۡوَٰلِدَانِ وَٱلۡأَقۡرَبُونَ مِمَّا قَلَّ مِنۡهُ أَوۡ كَثُرَۚ </div><div>نَصِيبٗا</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div><a data-content='واجبًا أو مُقْتَطعا محدودا' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>مَّفۡرُوضٗا</a> ٧ وَإِذَا حَضَرَ ٱلۡقِسۡمَةَ أُوْلُواْ ٱلۡقُرۡبَىٰ وَٱلۡيَتَٰمَىٰ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'></div><div>وَٱلۡيَتَٰمَىٰ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>وَٱلۡمَسَٰكِينُ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> فَٱرۡزُقُوهُم مِّنۡهُ وَقُولُواْ لَهُمۡ قَوۡلٗا </div><div>مَّعۡرُوفٗا</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>٨</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> وَلۡيَخۡشَ ٱلَّذِينَ لَوۡ تَرَكُواْ مِنۡ خَلۡفِهِمۡ ذُرِّيَّةٗ </div><div>ضِعَٰفًا</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>خَافُواْ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> عَلَيۡهِمۡ فَلۡيَتَّقُواْ ٱللَّهَ وَلۡيَقُولُواْ <a data-content='جميلاً أو صوابًا وعدْلاً' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>قَوۡلٗا سَدِيدًا</a> ٩ </div><div>إِنَّ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>ٱلَّذِينَ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> يَأۡكُلُونَ أَمۡوَٰلَ ٱلۡيَتَٰمَىٰ ظُلۡمًا إِنَّمَا